Manatee Festival January 2019
32nd Annual Florida Manatee Festival
& Rotary Craft Fair !
January 2019
Saturday 01/19/2019 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.
Sunday 01/20/2019 9:00 a.m. to 4:00 p.m.
Come, Celebrate, Relax
Surround yourself with the natural beauty of Crystal River and the warmth of the community. Located in historic downtown Crystal River, one can experience the thrill of interacting with the West Indian Manatee in its natural
habitat.

*FELLOWSHIP* Halloween Party
Event Name: *FELLOWSHIP* Halloween Party
Description: 10/21/2011
Halloween party at Candy and Billy Sasser’s
Oct 21st Halloween Party at Billy and Candy Sasser’s complete with Costume Contest.  Event will start at 6pm and the Club will provide turkey/ham and we ask everyone to bring a covered dish along with BYOB.
6650 W CONESTOGA ST BEVERLY HILLS (PINE RIDGE)
Location: 6650 W CONESTOGA ST BEVERLY HILLS
FROM CR. GO 486 TO A LEFT ONTO PINE RIDGE BLVD TO A LEFT ON BUCKSKIN TO A LEFT ON CIMARRON RIGHT ON BUFFALO TO A LEFT ON CONESTOGA.  HOME AT END OF CUL DE SAC.
http://maps.google.com/maps?saddr=Crystal+River,+FL&daddr=W+Conestoga+Dr&hl=en&sll=28.947302,-82.544317&sspn=0.00982,0.019205&geocode=FU8EuQEdp7wT-ymXtELydlnoiDG7RgmzNeq5kA%3BFXS3uQEd3HMU-w&mra=ls&vpsrc=0&z=13

2010 February STOP HUNGER NOW
Click here to view Slideshow:
http://crystalriverrotary.com/?page_id=258&album=9
ROTARY WORKS TO STOP HUNGER By Sharon Harris
If you believe that with over 6.6 billion people in the world there just isn’t enough food to go around so it’s impossible to stop world hunger, Rotarians will tell you that you are wrong. Citrus County Rotarians are teaming with Rotarians around the world to help end the scourge of hunger.
